environment<ul><li>in the 3 years that precede the application for the Flemish recognition certificate, the applicant has not been convicted of a criminal offence in a member state of the European Economic Area, for infringements of the environmental legislation concerning the use of the recognition.</li><li>in the 2 years that precede the application for the Flemish recognition certificate, no recognition with the same object was revoked due to infringement of the obligations associated with that recognition.</li></ul></li><li><strong>special recognition conditions</strong>:<ul><li>have sound procedures in place to organise the examination</li><li>have suitable technical personnel</li><li>organise a regulatory examination jury.</li></ul></li></ul><h2>Validity period and obligations<strong> </strong></h2><p>The recognition is valid for an <strong>indefinite period</strong>. The training centre must meet the following obligations among others to retain recognition:</p><ul><li>provide quality training</li><li>guarantee objectivity and independence</li><li>organise training and examinations as prescribed</li><li>have the necessary infrastructure in place to organise the examination</li><li>award certificates and submit the examination file to the competent authorities</li><li>hold insurance for third-party liability, including professional liability, in connection with the use of the recognition</li></ul>"},"naam":{"en":"Requirements","nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"Voorwaarden","nl-BE-x-generated-formal":"Voorwaarden","nl":"Voorwaarden"},"@type":"Voorwaarde","order":0}],"procedures":[{"naam":{"nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"Procedure","nl":"Procedure","en":"Procedure","nl-BE-x-generated-formal":"Procedure"},"beschrijving":{"nl-BE-x-generated-informal":"<p>Vraag jouw erkenning aan bij de Vlaamse overheid.</p><ul><li>Download het aanvraagformulier en vul het in:<ul><li><a href=\"https://assets.vlaanderen.be/raw/upload/v1653999848/191004_Aanvraag_tot_erkenning_als_opleidings